1
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:05,640
Come catch me.

2
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,160
Come here.

3
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:10,920
The Prince is over here.

4
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,680
Whoever gets caught,

5
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,920
belongs to me.

6
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:18,940
Your Highness.

7
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,200
Come on.

8
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:20,800
Over here.

9
00:01:22,039 --> 00:01:22,520
Come here.

10
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,520
Where are you?

11
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:24,640
Come on.

12
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,039
I'm over here.

13
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:29,160
Caught you.

14
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,759
It's you.

15
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:36,039
Are you surprised, Prince?

16
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:37,200
Drink my wine.

17
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,920
Aren't you afraid I poisoned it?

18
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,600
Would you really?

19
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:45,400
Leave us.

20
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,000
Walking in like this,

21
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:54,060
means you've accepted your fate and are willing to be my woman?

22
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,680
I am here to make a deal with you, Prince.

23
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,320
A deal?

24
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,680
Don't you know

25
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:07,560
that your father has already sold you to me?

26
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,199
Framing the Song Army,

27
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:12,100
and luring them into the trap... that was all me.

28
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:15,520
Prince, doing business with a fool,

29
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,260
what good will that do you?

30
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,440
I like smart women.

31
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:29,340
Marquis Bai and Song Xuan are obstacles to your rule over Dasheng.

32
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,579
Make a deal with me,

33
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:33,440
and I guarantee they will die.

34
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,360
Then what do you want?

35
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,760
My father's life.

36
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:48,280
But I've already promised Chancellor Shen.

37
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,680
I can't go back on my word.

38
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,240
Prince,

39
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,820
dead men's words don't count.

40
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,520
Then...

41
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,880
what if you betray me?

42
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:14,170
I was never yours to begin with,

43
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,820
so how can I betray you?

44
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,920
The bet is on.

45
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,480
If you choose the Bai family,

46
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,360
I'll lose everything.

47
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,690
Anyway, you don't have much time left.

48
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,930
Don't come over!

49
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:45,600
Don't!

50
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,760
Should we call the Marquis back?

51
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,400
Maybe we should call the Marquis back.

52
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,560
No, the Marquis has been at the Palace these past few days.

53
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,160
He has more important things to do.

54
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,680
Young Master! Young Master!

55
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,880
Young Master, bad news!

56
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:58,360
There are so many people outside.

57
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,080
It's the families of the children who died at the academy,

58
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,540
along with some riffraff.

59
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:04,760
They're calling out by name, demanding Marquis Zhongyi's Manor hand over Miss Chuyi.

60
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:05,760
They also said...

61
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,760
Said what?

62
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,040
They said Miss is a bastard,

63
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,580
a jinx, and she must pay with her life.

64
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,360
Nonsense!

65
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:15,000
Who allowed them to behave so atrociously in front of the Manor?

66
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,160
Why didn't you stop them?

67
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,680
We tried, but we couldn't stop them.

68
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,160
We couldn't drive them away either.

69
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,040
They just keep saying they're delivering justice for Heaven.

70
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,960
They even called Marquis Zhongyi's Manor a cesspool of filth,

71
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,400
specially sheltering monsters.

72
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,930
Alright, go watch the gate.

73
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:29,800
I didn't kill anyone.

74
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,600
I didn't.

75
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,720
I didn't kill anyone.

76
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:35,600
Chuyi.

77
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:36,240
I'm not...

78
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,080
Chuyi.

79
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,920
I'm not a monster.

80
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,720
Of course you aren't.

81
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,440
Chuyi.

82
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:40,560
What's wrong?

83
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,000
Chuyi.

84
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,400
I'm not a monster.

85
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:46,960
I'm not.

86
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:47,360
Chuyi.

87
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,000
I'm not.

88
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,200
Princess.

89
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,800
Princess. Princess.

90
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,200
Stay with me. Look at me.

91
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,600
Princess, snap out of it.

92
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,520
Princess.

93
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:11,120
What on earth is going on?

94
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:14,560
The Wolf King's blood is boiling inside the Princess.

95
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,120
I've heard of this.

96
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:19,520
The Yueshi royal family possesses the power of the Wolf King.

97
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,560
It manifests after they come of age.

98
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,560
Before that,

99
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:23,680
they must learn

100
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,640
how to control and use this power.

101
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,640
But isn't that after coming of age?

102
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:28,840
Chuyi is still young.

103
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:32,760
So her transformation isn't natural.

104
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,960
Someone must have tampered with her.

105
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:37,200
That's because someone used witchcraft

106
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:40,200
to forcibly trigger the Wolf King's power within her.

107
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,460
How can we break it?

108
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,890
This witchcraft is extremely subtle.

109
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,560
It hides within the Princess's body.

110
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,800
Whenever her emotions are intensely stimulated,

111
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,530
it triggers.

112
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,680
I can only suppress it temporarily.

113
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,920
I cannot break it.

114
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,480
If this witchcraft remains in Chuyi's body,

115
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:57,440
besides fainting like this,

116
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,080
will there be other effects?

117
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:01,520
As long as the witchcraft remains,

118
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:04,160
every time the Princess's sanity takes a hit,

119
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,440
the Wolf King's power inside her

120
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:07,680
will further devour her consciousness.

121
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,540
If this goes on,

122
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,770
sooner or later,

123
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,520
the Princess will become a monster

124
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,650
and never turn back.

125
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:13,780
This...

126
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:15,920
Then how can we root it out?

127
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:18,640
There is only one way to root it out.

128
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:22,960
The caster must die.

129
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,920
Bai Chuyi.

130
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,680
Just a few more days,

131
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,500
and your destiny will become my fortune.

132
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,760
By then, the throne,

133
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,480
the bloodline, everything will be mine.

134
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,320
Long time no see, Miss Song.

135
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:01,440
Miss Shen, what brings you here?

136
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,640
I heard Chuyi is unconscious.

137
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,840
I came to check on her.

138
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,720
Lingbo is knowledgeable.

139
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,520
Perhaps she can find something.

140
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,520
This is witchcraft.

141
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,040
You know of it?

142
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,520
I've heard a little about it.

143
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:23,440
Do you know who cast it?

144
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:27,080
I'm afraid only one person in the capital can cast this spell.

145
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:28,520
Princess Tuoya.

146
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,860
Are you so certain, Miss Shen?

147
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:35,610
I wouldn't joke about Manchuan's sister's life.

148
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:39,159
Manchuan, if you need help,

149
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,520
just tell me anytime.

150
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:42,050
I'm willing to do anything.

151
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:46,140
If you really want to help, Miss Shen,

152
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:47,040
why don't you tell us

153
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,970
how you know about this witchcraft

154
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,650
and how you know it's Tuoya?

155
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:54,000
Not everything in this world is a coincidence.

156
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,920
It's just that I've been investigating.

157
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,980
I care about Chuyi,

158
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,159
and I care about

159
00:07:59,040 --> 00:07:59,560
you.

160
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,060
Then you should look into, Miss Shen,

161
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:05,140
the matter of the 500,000 taels of army provisions.

162
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,160
What do you mean by that, Miss Song?

163
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,890
You know what I mean, Miss Shen.

164
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:14,600
Lingbo,

165
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,240
regarding Chuyi,

166
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,500
if you can really help,

167
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,850
then I trust you.

168
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:22,440
I understand. I will help.

169
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,080
Manchuan,

170
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:29,080
I hope you don't trust the wrong person.

171
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,120
What do you think of her?

172
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:39,240
I think she must be connected to Tuoya.

173
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:42,059
Otherwise, she wouldn't have said that.

174
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,570
Will you still test her?

175
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,080
No need.

176
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,770
She is no longer the Shen Lingbo she used to be.

177
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,000
Shen Lingbo,

178
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:05,720
why did you bring me to such a foul place?

179
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,080
Don't put on airs with me.

180
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,280
If you want to live,

181
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,600
do as I say.

182
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:13,040
I don't know what you're talking about.

183
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,560
Father came to see you, didn't he?

184
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,960
What exactly do you want?

185
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,980
Give this letter to the Third Prince.

186
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:24,640
Tell him everything you know about Father's plot.

187
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,960
You want me to betray Father?

188
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,280
He treated you as a sacrifice long ago.

189
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,480
If you don't save yourself,

190
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,140
no one will.

191
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,200
How can you do this?

192
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,280
He is our father!

193
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:38,200
He is the Prime Minister.

194
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,280
He is a traitor.

195
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,200
He can be anyone,

196
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:43,170
but he cannot be our father.

197
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,450
Don't delude yourself.

198
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,880
Then why help me?

199
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,140
Because you are still useful.

200
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:54,640
Get the Emperor to give the Dasheng Token to the Third Prince,

201
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:57,080
then tell the Third Prince to go to the Marquis of Zhongyi's Manor.

202
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:57,760
I won't go.

203
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,560
You must.

204
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:02,200
What if the Third Prince doesn't believe me?

205
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,200
Then you will die.

206
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:07,200
What?

207
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:08,720
Scared?

208
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,160
If you are scared,

209
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,280
you can go ahead and burn the letter,

210
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,010
then go back and kill yourself.

211
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:18,020
Maybe you'll die with a bit more dignity.

212
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:19,420
I'll go.

213
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,600
Don't let me down.
